data.description: Take a look at this 20.12 acre mini-ranchette with soaring Salmon River Canyon views located below the hard snow line. The 1999 Fleetwood manufactured home is 1716 sq ft and boasts 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 baths, vaulted ceilings, a living and large family room, split bedroom design, two covered decks and automatic sprinklers. Need parking or room for toy storage? Enjoy a newly built 1440 sq ft shop w/ roll-up doors and a 24 x 22 carport. The 26 x 36 pole barn and fenced pasture will accommodate all your livestock. Resident elk, deer, turkey and upland birds frequent property. There is a deer fenced garden area, apple, cherry, pear and plum trees on the property. New metal roof in 2021 and newly installed gutters throughout. This is located in Whitewater Wilderness Ranch Subdivision where land owners have exclusive access through a locked gate to access USFS ground for hunting, hiking, mushroom picking, horseback riding and more! BTVAI
